Package com.controller

Class RoomServiceControl

java.lang.Object
com.controller.RoomServiceControl
All Implemented Interfaces:
CreatorController<RoomService>
public class RoomServiceControl extends Object implements CreatorController<RoomService>
RoomServiceControl.java A controller class that realises the CreatorController interface. It consists of methods that will enable its users to control the outcome of a RoomService object.
